long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension is designed to challenge and sharpen your data structures and algorithms skills right from your new tab page.

Every time you open a new tab, a fresh and randomly selected data structures or algorithms question will greet you.

Combining over 250 questions from GeeksforGeeks, LeetCode this extension makes sure that a variety of questions needed for your interview preparation is there.

 Features:-

• Randomized Questions: Every time you open a new tab, a fresh and randomly selected data structures or algorithms question will greet you. Say goodbye to mundane new tab pages and embrace the excitement of learning something new each day.

• Combining questions from GeeksforGeeks, Leetcode, Striver's SDE Sheet, 450 DSA Sheet by Love Babbar, this extension makes sure that a variety of questions needed for your interview preparation is there.

• Problem Types: This extension provides an extensive array of challenges focused on data structures and algorithms. You'll tackle problems involving arrays, linked lists, trees, graphs, sorting methods, searching strategies, and beyond.
